lyrics:
Ngai r'u, rawngbawltu zawng zawngte u,
Chak lo leh thidangin;
Lalpa duhawm i nghak reng ang u,
Min tichak thar zel ang.

Lalpa nghaktu apiangte chu,
An lo chak thar ang;
Thlain an han thawk ang,
Mu angin thlain an thlawk chho vang;
Hah lovin an tlan fo vang,
Thidang lovin an kal ang;
Hah lovin an tlan fo vang,
Chau tawh lovin an kal ang;
Hah lovin an tlan chak fo vang;
Chau lovin an kal.

Vawi tam tak ningin leh lungngaiiin,
A chungah kan phunnawi;
Chhandamtu nung leh ropui kan ring,
Engah nge kan thihdan?

Lawm r'u, kan hnenah a awm reng ang,
Khawvel tawp thleng pawhin;
Ding r'u, kal zel turin zuam rawh u,
Thatna khawp a tir ang.
